  "time_ut": 1662075445,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dc5\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc1\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd3 \u0dbd\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9a\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0dba\u0da7 \u0d85\u0db8\u0dad\u0dbb \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1\u0da7 \u0dc4\u0dad\u0d9a \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dba\u0daf\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The fuel problem cost the Sri Lankan service an additional seven million",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "By not providing fuel to the aircraft, the oil corporation has to incur an additional loss of seven million US dollars per month due to the fact that the aircraft of the Sri Lankan Airlines are getting the fuel they need from India.",
        "This loss is estimated to cover the cost of traveling to and from India to purchase fuel and depreciation of fuel and aircraft.",
        "It is said that between twenty-five and thirty planes go to India every month to get oil. A spokesperson of SriLankan Airlines said that this flight is an additional journey and the depreciation of the aircraft will affect it in the long term.",
        "About 550,000 liters of aviation fuel is required per day."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "the Sri Lankan",
          "label": "LOC"
        },
        {
          "text": "an additional seven million",
